dc_title_s: Mapa geologico de Guatemala = Geological map of Guatemala. San Jose Pinula, hoja 2159 IV G
dc_description_s: Guatemala. Instituto Geografico Nacional. North Decimal Degree 14.666700. South Decimal Degree 14.5000. East Decimal Degree -90.2500. West Decimal Degree -90.5000. Alternate title: Mapa geologico = Geologic map: San Jose Pinula, Guatemala. Universal transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 20 m. with supplementary 10 m. contour interval and spot heights. "El levantamiento geologico se efectuo en 1969, 1970, y 1971 dentro de un programa colaborativo entre Dartmouth College de New Hampshire, Estados Unidos de America y el Instituto Geografico Nacional.".
